    <p class="long-text">Web apps are so widely used now that it is basically essential to develop web apps as a programmer.  &nbsp;When writing web apps I work primarily in the 
      <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/" target="blank" class="long-text">Ruby on Rails</a> framework which requires a strong knowledge of 
      <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML" target="blank" class="long-text">HTML</a>, 
      <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cascading_Style_Sheets" target="blank" class="long-text">CSS</a>, 
