      <a href="https://www.ruby-lang.org/en/" target="blank" class="long-text">Ruby</a>.</p>
    <p class="long-text">For projects that don't require the amount of power that rails gives you, I prefer <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/" target="blank" class="long-text">Sinatra</a> as a light-weight framework that still gives you many of the advantages that come with using Ruby as a web-development language</p>
